01:30:00.060 --> 01:30:02.430
in uninsured Americans.

01:30:02.430 --> 01:30:06.000
And that despite the assumption
that Medicaid is broken,

01:30:06.000 --> 01:30:07.950
many of the patients
who receive it

01:30:07.950 --> 01:30:10.170
